<TEXT>
<P>
JAKARTA, August 21 (Xinhua) -- Indonesia said Friday it feels
"deep concern" about the implications of the bomb blasts at
American embassies in Kenya and Tanzania but disapproves of any
intervention in and aggression against sovereign countries to
fight terrorism.
</P>
<P>
