<HEADLINE> Philippine Rebel Group Renews Mass Indoctrination </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MANILA, August 21 (Xinhua) -- The Philippines' leftist rebel
group, the New People's Army (NPA), has renewed its massive
indoctrination in the countryside to regain some foothold in their
mass base organization, the military said Friday.
</P>
