<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, August 21 (Xinhua) -- "Beijing Cultural Hot Lines," a
public Web site, became operational here today to help Internet
surfers look up information about the capital's culture,
libraries, online cinemas and tourist resorts.
</P>
