<HEADLINE> EU Holds No Official Position on U.S. Attacks </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BRUSSELS, August 21 (Xinhua) -- A European Commission official
said Friday that the commission had no official position on
Thursday's attacks by the United States on Afghanistan and Sudan.
</P>
