President Joseph Estrada stressed the need for NGOs and
international funding agencies' participation in providing social
services, particularly to the marginalized sectors.
</P>
<P>
"Our performance in poverty alleviation does not compare well
with other countries in East Asia and the Asia Pacific region," he
told NGO representatives, heads of international funding agencies
and members of the diplomatic corps at the ceremony.
</P>
<P>
