<HEADLINE> Frenchman Wins Fourth Race in Gold Cup </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ATHENS, August 20 (Xinhua) -- Frenchman Xavier Rohart won the
fourth race of the Finn Gold Cup world championship on Thursday
to move into third place on the leaderboard.
</P>
