until the sworn-in ceremony scheduled for Saturday, the report
said.
</P>
<P>
Following the sudden death of Abacha on June 8 and that of
detained opposition leader Moshood Abiola, Abubakar has announced
the release of all political detainees and the annulment of all
elections held under Abacha's transition to civil rule program.
</P>
<P>
The move won Abubakar the trust of the country's opposition as
well as the western countries which have imposed sanctions
against Nigeria for its poor human rights record.
</P>
