facing would not affect the Middle East peace process, referring
to the legal battle against Clinton over his affair with a former
White House intern.
</P>
<P>
Palestinian officials have voiced concern that the Mideast
peace process is paying the price for the sex scandal.
</P>
<P>
The Israeli-Palestinian peace process has been stalled since
early last due to Israel's expansion of settlements and repeated
delay in carrying out the next stage of troop withdrawal from the
West Bank.
</P>
<P>
The U.S. has failed to persuade Israel to accept a proposal on
a further 13.1 percent West Bank withdrawal in return for stronger
Palestinian security guarantees. 
