<HEADLINE> Tunis Stock Exchange Index Up </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TUNIS, August 20 (Xinhua) -- The index of Tunis Stock Exchange
closed at 459.98 points on Thursday, up from Wednesday's finish of
458.40.
</P>
